data.description: Freshly Updated home on over 1 acre in a NO HOA Neighborhood - Walnut Grove District. 3BR plus bonus room/office and 2 Full bathrooms and well as an extended garage with workout space or 2nd office AND 2nd Outbuilding/workshop behind Home. Fenced in Back yard with Pool, and Screened in porch with additional back porch overlooking pool and serene private back yard. Courtyard with access from the VERY large Laundry/Mudroom into the back yard keeps all parts of the home with access to the fantastic yard. Separate 2nd Living Room with large bay window and separate dining and eat in sunroom kitchen keep this home with lots of space and room for everyone. We are priced WELL Below Market Value and Neighborhood comps as this home is priced to sell. Pool liner is 1 years old and Pump is 1 years old. NO diving board, Professional cover on pool has hooks into the concrete and has been in place the start of this fall. 2 HVAC Units work and keep home very cool and heated throughout all seasons. Updated Counter Tops in the kitchen and breakfast room help keep the home clean and move in ready. Seller offer 5k in closing cost and 1 year home warranty.
